  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>​​Rinse your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> until the water runs clear, then add it to a pot with a lid with 175ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [230ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked, then remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1634028559080-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1634028559080-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1634028559080-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1634028559080-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1634028559080-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, wash and shred your<strong> lettuce</strong> finely, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Top, tail, peel, then grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> to a large mixing bowl</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1634028563097-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1634028563097-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1634028563097-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1634028563097-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1634028563097-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong> cucumber </strong>into discs</p><p>Slice each individual <strong>cucumber disc</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Cut <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into rounds (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Add the<strong> cucumber matchsticks</strong> and <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the bowl with the lettuce,<strong> </strong>carrot and spring onion – this is your <strong>crunchy salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1634028567385-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1634028567385-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
